#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Czorgtoeslag-cross-org-journey.md:1
msgid "User guide: applying for zorgtoeslag via Unive"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Czorgtoeslag-cross-org-journey.md:3
msgid ""
"This guide walks through the complete end-to-end journey for the AWB "
"zorgtoeslag cross-organisation scenario. No prior knowledge of the platform "
"is needed — follow the steps in order."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Czorgtoeslag-cross-org-journey.md:5
msgid ""
"**What this demonstrates:** A citizen logs into a private insurer's (Unive) "
"portal, calculates their zorgtoeslag entitlement, submits a formal AWB "
"application, and receives a decision — all without leaving the Unive "
"environment. The application is handled by a Dienst Toeslagen caseworker on "
"the government side."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Czorgtoeslag-cross-org-journey.md:7
msgid "**Environment:** [https://acc.mijn.open-regels.nl]{1}"
msgstr ""

