#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Czorgtoeslag-cross-org-journey.md:47
msgid ""
"Click **Berekenen**. The result card shows whether there is entitlement and "
"the estimated annual and monthly amounts."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Czorgtoeslag-cross-org-journey.md:54
msgid "2b — Submit the application"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Czorgtoeslag-cross-org-journey.md:56
msgid ""
"Click **Aanvragen**. The view switches to the **Zorgtoeslag aanvragen** "
"card, which renders the deployed `zorgtoeslag-provisional-start` form via "
"the Operaton process definition. The form fields are pre-filled from the "
"values you entered in the calculator. Review the pre-filled values and "
"submit the form to start the `AwbZorgtoeslagProcess`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Czorgtoeslag-cross-org-journey.md:63
msgid ""
"After submission a success card appears showing the **dossiernummer**. The "
"process is now running under Dienst Toeslagen (`municipality = toeslagen`)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Czorgtoeslag-cross-org-journey.md:72
msgid "Step 3 — Process the application as the Toeslagen caseworker"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Czorgtoeslag-cross-org-journey.md:74
msgid ""
"Open a new browser session (incognito or a different browser) and go to "
"[https://acc.mijn.open-regels.nl]{1}. Click **Inloggen als medewerker** on "
"the login choice screen and enter the following credentials:"
msgstr ""

